text: The 2020 United States presidential election in Delaware was held on Tuesday, November 3, 2020, as part of the 2020 United States presidential election. Former Vice President Joe Biden and his running mate U.S. SenatorKamala Harrishad won 3 electoral votes in the Electoral College. == References == Category:2020 United States presidential election Category:2020s in Delaware
title: 2020 United States presidential election in Delaware
